(150, 'Boxes for Hotels and Spas', 'boxes-for-hotels-and-spas', 'Boxes for Hotels and Spas', 'Boxes for Hotels and Spas', 'Boxes for Hotels and Spas', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur in placerat odio. Maecenas eu vestibulum sapien. Nulla vitae tellus quis magna consequat aliquet. Sed tortor est, accumsan eget venenatis sed, condimentum a elit. Nullam mollis fringilla maximus. Mauris a dignissim mauris, ut volutpat lectus. Quisque hendrerit, odio sit amet eleifend dictum, ligula purus mollis sapien, nec consequat nibh neque vitae dolor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">In tempor fermentum quam non molestie. Nullam nec congue nisi, tempor congue nunc. Vivamus ac mollis mauris. Maecenas rhoncus tempor convallis. Quisque ultricies auctor rutrum. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nam id arcu in eros suscipit lacinia. Sed nec porta metus. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Integer facilisis faucibus arcu sit amet posuere.</p>', 'boxes-for-hotels-and-spas-printing.jpg', 'Boxes for Hotels and Spas', '[\"boxes-for-hotels-and-spas.jpg\",\"boxes-for-hotels-and-spas-printing.jpg\",\"custom-boxes-for-hotels-and-spas-printing.jpg\",\"printed-boxes-for-hotels-and-spas.jpg\"]', 64, '[\"151\",\"152\",\"153\"]', 1, 0),
(151, 'Bangle Boxes', 'bangle-boxes', 'Bangle Boxes', 'Bangle Boxes', 'Bangle Boxes', '<p>Bangle Boxes</p>', '<p>Bangle Boxes</p>', 'bangle-storage-solutions.jpg', 'Bangle Boxes', '[\"bangle-boxes.jpg\",\"bangle-gift-box.jpg\",\"bangle-jewellery-box.jpg\",\"bangle-storage-solutions.jpg\"]', 64, '[\"150\",\"152\",\"153\"]', 1, 0),
(152, 'Boxes for Belts', 'boxes-for-belts', 'Boxes for Belts', 'Boxes for Belts', 'Boxes for Belts', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>', NULL, 'gift-boxes-for-belt.jpg', 'Boxes for Belts', '[\"boxes-for-belt.jpg\",\"boxes-for-belts.jpg\",\"gift-boxes-for-belt.jpg\",\"packaging-boxes-for-belts.jpg\"]', 64, '[\"150\",\"151\",\"153\"]', 1, 0),
(153, 'Business Card Boxes', 'business-card-boxes', 'Business card boxes are the need of every corporate sector. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes with various customizations and free shipping.', 'Business Card Boxes', 'Business Card Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Every business, smaller or larger, needs business card boxes. These boxes are made with rigid materials such as kraft and corrugated stocks. Different types of printing and finishing techniques are used to make these boxes more presentable. CMYK and PMS color schemes are used for the printing of these boxes. Brand logo and customized text can also be added to these boxes to make them appropriate for a certain occasion. Additional customizations such as a die-cut window, placeholder, and insert can also be added to these boxes.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes is among the leading packaging manufacturing suppliers in the United States of America. With over a decade of experience, we claim to provide the finest packaging solutions with unmatchable features.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Get the Lowest Pricing</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We always strive to provide the clients with the finest business card packaging at affordable pricing. We keep our prices the lowest to facilitate every client. Also, we offer special volume discounts on larger orders.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>End to End Customizations</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers various customization options for&nbsp;<strong>custom business card boxes</strong>. The clients can choose the customizable size, shape, style, and design of these boxes. The clients can also make a choice of the manufacturing material, its thickness, and color scheme. Also, there are a number of finishing styles available for these boxes, including matte, gloss, soft-touch, smudge-free, and foiling.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-quality Printing</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest technologies for the printing of&nbsp;<strong>business card boxes</strong>. The clients can choose the type of printing as per their preference or seek professional assistance from us as well. Also, we offer complimentary design support to the clients for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping &amp; Order Tracking</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer free delivery of these boxes across the United States of America and Canada. Clients from other regions of the world can also get these boxes delivered on demand. Rush shipping option is also available on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Eco-friendly Packaging</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes understands the corporate social responsibility to nature. All the products, including boxes, banners, and other items, are manufactured with 100 percent biodegradable and recyclable supplies.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customer Care Service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides professional assistance to clients via different channels. We respond to our clients at the earliest via our dedicated chat portal, call, and e-mail. A call-back request is also an option to reach us.</span></p>', 'business-card-boxes.jpg', 'Mailer-&-Corrugated-Boxes', '[\"business-card-boxes.jpg\",\"business-card-boxes-cardboard.jpg\",\"business-card-box-organizer.jpg\",\"custom-business-card-boxes.jpg\"]', 64, '[\"150\",\"151\",\"152\"]', 1, 0),
(158, 'Cardboard Boxes', 'cardboard-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes manufactures the most affordable cardboard boxes in the USA. Our boxes are perfect for every business.', 'Cardboard Boxes, Eco-friendly Packaging, cardboard boxes for moving, Cardboard Packaging, Cardboard Boxes with Lids', 'Cardboard Boxes | Eco-friendly Packaging, PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Cardboard Boxes&nbsp;are the most commonly used packaging solutions in the world. They are popular because of their adaptability for all businesses. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes with a number of customization options. The customization options include the choice of size, shape, color scheme, and type of lamination. The shape of these boxes varies following the needs of the products. PremiumBoxes uses organic and recyclable supplies for the manufacturing of these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Lowest pricing in the USA</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes claims to offer these boxes at the lowest pricing in the United States of America. Our pricing accommodates the clients from different businesses and helps them get the finest packaging solutions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Get Customized Boxes</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the most flexible customization options. Our product range includes all types of packaging solutions. We also offer&nbsp;<strong>cardboard boxes for moving</strong>&nbsp;to both fresh and established businesses.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Advanced Printing Technology</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use the latest printing technologies for the printing of our products. Design support service along with 2D or 3D mockups are offered as per the client&rsquo;s demands.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Striking Finishing Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Finishing options such as spot UV, soft-touch, smudge-free, and watermark are available for all our products to make them exceptionally remarkable.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Eco-friendly Packaging</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes fulfills the corporate social responsibility towards the environment. All our products are made with 100 percent organic and biodegradable materials. Plant-based inks are used for the printing of our products.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Our Exclusive Features</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers various services that make it stand out among its competitors. Some of the features are listed below;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free design support</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free shipping in North America</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Vigilant customer care</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Easy and secure payment options</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">No die-cut or plate charges</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'cardboard-gift-boxes.jpg', 'Cardboard Boxes', '[\"cardboard-boxes.jpg\",\"cardboard-boxes-for-moving.jpg\",\"cardboard-gift-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-cardboard-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"218\",\"219\",\"220\",\"225\"]', 1, 0),
(159, 'CBD Boxes', 'cbd-boxes', 'CBD Boxes', 'CBD Boxes', 'CBD Boxes', '<p>CBD Boxes</p>', '<p>CBD Boxes</p>', 'cbd-boxes.jpg', 'CBD Boxes', '[\"cbd-boxes.jpg\",\"cbd-box-packaging.jpg\",\"cbd-product-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-cbd-boxes.jpg\"]', 83, '[\"160\",\"161\",\"162\",\"163\"]', 1, 0),
(160, 'CBD Oil Packaging', 'cbd-oil-packaging', 'CBD Oil Packaging', 'CBD Oil Packaging', 'CBD Oil Packaging', '<p>CBD Oil Packaging</p>', '<p>CBD Oil Packaging</p>', 'hemp-oil-packaging.jpg', 'CBD Oil Packaging', '[\"beard-oil-packaging.jpg\",\"cbd-oil-packaging.jpg\",\"hemp-oil-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-cbd-oil-packaging.jpg\"]', 83, '[\"159\",\"161\",\"162\",\"163\"]', 1, 0),
(161, 'E-Cigarette Boxes', 'e-cigarette-boxes', 'E-Cigarette Boxes', 'E-Cigarette Boxes', 'E-Cigarette Boxes', '<p>E-Cigarette Boxes</p>', '<p>E-Cigarette Boxes</p>', 'e-cigarette-boxes.jpg', 'E-Cigarette Boxes', '[\"custom-e-cigarette-boxes.jpg\",\"e-cigarette-boxes.jpg\",\"e-cigarette-liquid-packaging.jpg\",\"electronic-cigarettes-boxes.jpg\"]', 83, '[\"159\",\"160\",\"162\",\"163\"]', 1, 0),
(162, 'Vape Packaging', 'vape-packaging', 'Vape Packaging', 'Vape Packaging', 'Vape Packaging', '<p>Vape Packaging</p>', '<p>Vape Packaging</p>', 'vape-packaging.jpg', 'Vape Packaging', '[\"custom-vape-packaging.jpg\",\"vape-cartridge-boxes.jpg\",\"vape-cartridge-packaging.jpg\",\"vape-packaging.jpg\"]', 83, '[\"159\",\"160\",\"161\",\"163\"]', 1, 0),
(163, 'Cannabis Boxes', 'cannabis-boxes', 'Cannabis Boxes', 'Cannabis Boxes', 'Cannabis Boxes', '<p>Cannabis Boxes</p>', '<p>Cannabis Boxes</p>', 'cannabis-boxes.jpg', 'Cannabis Boxes', '[\"cannabis-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-cannabis-boxes.jpg\",\"medical-cannabis-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-cannabis-boxes.jpg\"]', 83, '[\"159\",\"160\",\"161\",\"162\"]', 1, 0),
(164, 'Cream Boxes', 'cream-boxes', 'Cream boxes are an essential need of cosmetics companies. PremiumBoxes offers a diverse range of these boxes with a number of customizations.', 'Beauty Boxes, Cream Boxes, cream packaging boxes, cream packaging, Cosmetic Boxes, Cosmetic Packaging, printed cream boxes', 'Cream Boxes | Cream Storage Boxes, Beauty Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Cream Boxes&nbsp;are a popular choice of cosmetics brands. Various materials like cardboard stock or Kraft stock are mostly used to manufacture these boxes. PremiumBoxes provides plenty of customization options to make them look fascinating. Clients have the option to select the style, size, and shape of these boxes. Excellent printing techniques are used to enhance their visuals. The option of adding a die-cut window or a handle is also available.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Enticing Customizations</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Custom cream boxes</strong>&nbsp;are high in demand for the growing cosmetics industry. PremiumBoxes provides these boxes with various customization options to make them according to the requirements of the clients. The customization options include the choice of shape, size, style, and manufacturing material.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Versatile Materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses eco-friendly materials for manufacturing&nbsp;<strong>cream packaging boxes</strong>. The options of manufacturing materials include; cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks. The clients can choose the material as well as its thickness for&nbsp;<strong>cream boxes</strong>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Best Customer Care:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our customer service professionals are available for clients at every step. Clients can contact us through email, dedicated chat portal, and call.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Remarkable Finishing Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides a wide range of finishing options for&nbsp;<strong>cream boxes</strong>. These options include matte, soft-touch, foiling, and gloss.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Economical Price</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the lowest price for&nbsp;<strong>printed cream boxes&nbsp;</strong>in the market. We have the latest technology to manufacture these boxes at a lower cost. Volume discounts are also available for large orders.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Quick Turnaround</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer the quickest turnaround time for&nbsp;<strong>cream packaging</strong>. Free shipping for clients across North America is available.</span></p>', 'cream-boxes.jpg', 'Cream Boxes', '[\"cream-boxes.jpg\",\"cream-gift-boxes.jpg\",\"cream-storage-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-cream-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"165\",\"166\",\"167\",\"168\"]', 1, 0),
(165, 'Eyeliner Boxes', 'eyeliner-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes manufactures eyeliner boxes with a number of customization options. Free shipping and free design support are also available.', 'Eyeliner Boxes, Customized Packaging, Printed eyeliner boxes, Cosmetic Packaging Boxes', 'Eyeliner Boxes | Customized Packaging, Printed eyeliner boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Eyeliner boxes are an essential part of the cosmetics industry. They are manufactured with organic supplies, including cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks. PremiumBoxes offers amazing customization options for these packaging solutions. The latest printing technologies, along with free design support, are available for the printing of these boxes. Any color scheme from CMYK and PMS color palettes can be used to make these packaging solutions more attractive and presentable. Lamination and waxing are also used to increase the safety level of these boxes.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Tons of Customization Options</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes is among the most elegant eyeliner packaging solutions suppliers. A large number of customization choices are offered to the clients to get the finest custom eyeliner boxes. The customization options include the choice of color scheme, size, design, shape, and style of these eyeliner boxes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Complimentary Design Assistance</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide complimentary professional assistance to the clients for printed eyeliner boxes designs. A free template of the design in 2D or 3D is also shared with the clients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Reasonable Pricing</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We strive to keep the pricing for custom eyeliner boxes the lowest in the market. Also, only secure and trusted channels are used for all payment transactions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free Delivery</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers free-of-cost delivery of eyeliner boxes across the United States of America and Canada. Shipping for clients worldwide is also available on request. Rush delivery of these packaging solutions is also available on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Professional Customer Care</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides professional assistance to the clients at every step. Get connected with us through calls, a dedicated chat portal, and e-mail.</span></p>', 'printed-cream-boxes.jpg', 'Eyeliner Boxes', '[\"custom-eyeliner-boxes.jpg\",\"eyeline-boxes.jpg\",\"eyeliner-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-cream-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"168\",\"169\",\"170\",\"171\"]', 1, 0),
(166, 'Eyeshadow Boxes', 'eyeshadow-boxes', 'Eyeshadow boxes are among the top-selling packaging solutions for the cosmetics industry. PremiumBoxes offers this packaging at the most economical pricing.', 'Eyeshadow Boxes', 'Eyeshadow Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Eyeshadow boxes&nbsp;</strong>are the essential need of various cosmetics brands. Organic materials such as cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks are used to manufacture them. PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques for these boxes. Various sizes and styles of these packaging solutions are available as per the requirements of clients. Finishing options such as smudge-free, matte, gloss, foil stamping, and many more are available. These boxes are available at the lowest pricing, along with volume discount options.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Eco-Friendly Materials</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses eco-friendly materials such as cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stock to manufacture these boxes. The inks used for the printing are also plant-based.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Striking Customization Options</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides the most flexible packaging solutions. Customization options for the shape, style and design of the&nbsp;<strong>custom eye shadow boxes&nbsp;</strong>are available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Enjoy Printing Techniques</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use the latest techniques to print these boxes. Color schemes including PMS and CMYK are used for the printing. We provide complimentary design support along with 2D or 3D mockups.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Enticing add-ons</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers a range of add-ons such as inserts, holders, and dividers for&nbsp;eyeshadow packaging<strong>. The clients can choose the add-ons as per their needs.</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Professional Customer Service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our customer care team is always available to assist the clients. We are available to the clients through call, live chat, and e-mail.</span></p>', 'eye-shadow-boxes.jpg', 'Eyeshadow Boxes', '[\"custom-eye-shadow-boxes.jpg\",\"eye-shadow-boxes.jpg\",\"eyeshadow-eyeshadow-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-eye-shadow-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"165\",\"174\",\"176\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(167, 'Foundation Boxes', 'foundation-boxes', 'Foundation boxes are essential for every cosmetic brand. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes at the lowest prices with free shipping in the USA and Canada.', 'Foundation Boxes', 'Foundation Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Foundation boxes&nbsp;showcase the quality of your products among the other competing brands. In addition, these boxes protect the items from rough handling. PremiumBoxes offers these packaging solutions at easily affordable prices. They are made of kraft, bux board, and cardboard materials. The inks, dyes, and adhesives used in the manufacturing of these boxes are also organic and safe for the natural environment. A wide range of color schemes from PMS and CMYK color palettes are used for the printing of these boxes. Free shipping and free design support are also available for these packaging solutions.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">In today&rsquo;s market, the packaging is one of the most important factors to boost sales. PremiumBoxes can provide&nbsp;<strong>customized foundation packaging boxes</strong>&nbsp;not only to protect the product but also to help captivate the potential customers at the same time.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Unique Shapes and Sizes:</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Unique shapes of&nbsp;<strong>foundation boxes&nbsp;</strong>can have a positive impact on the heart of customers and inspire them to go for purchasing the items immediately. Our ability to offer customized boxes gives us an edge over our competitors. Based on customer requirements, we can make changes to the style of the&nbsp;<strong>custom foundation boxes</strong>, such as adding a handle, die-cut windows, inserts, or placeholders.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Multiple Printing Methods:</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing methods and the finest materials to make sure customers receive top-of-the-line products at an affordable price. We use the latest printing methods such as digital, screen, and offset printings which gives results without any blur or removal effect.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Easily Affordable</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Due to current market competition, we understand that customers have the option to look around for the best pricing. We strive to keep our prices low without compromising on the quality of our products.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Quick Turnaround Time</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PrmeiumBoxes understands that the customer is the top priority. Dedicated team members are assigned to respond to customer inquiries from placing the order till the time the order reached their doorstep. Free shipping of these boxes is offered to clients across North America. Rush deliveries are also available.</span></p>', 'foundation-boxes.jpg', 'Foundation Boxes', '[\"custom-foundation-boxes.jpg\",\"foundation-boxes.jpg\",\"foundation-packaging-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-foundation-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"169\",\"171\",\"172\",\"175\"]', 1, 0),
(168, 'Hair Extension Boxes', 'hair-extension-boxes', 'Hair Extension Boxes', 'Hair Extension Boxes', 'Hair Extension Boxes', '<p>Hair Extension Boxes</p>', '<p>Hair Extension Boxes</p>', 'hair-extention-boxes.jpg', 'Hair Extension Boxes', '[\"custom-hair-boxes.jpg\",\"hair-extention-boxes.jpg\",\"hair-extention-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-hair-extention-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"169\",\"172\",\"174\",\"176\"]', 1, 0),
(169, 'Hairspray Boxes', 'hairspray-boxes', 'Hairspray Boxes', 'Hairspray Boxes', 'Hairspray Boxes', '<p>Hairspray Boxes</p>', '<p>Hairspray Boxes</p>', 'printed-hairspra-boxes.jpg', 'Hairspray Boxes', '[\"custom-hairspray-boxes.jpg\",\"hairspray-boxes.jpg\",\"hairspray-box-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-hairspra-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"166\",\"171\",\"172\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(170, 'Lip Balm Boxes', 'lip-balm-boxes', 'Lip Balm Boxes', 'Lip Balm Boxes', 'Lip Balm Boxes', '<p>Lip Balm Boxes</p>', '<p>Lip Balm Boxes</p>', 'printed-lip-balm-boxes.jpg', 'Lip Balm Boxes', '[\"lip-balm-boxes.jpg\",\"lip-balm-display-boxes.jpg\",\"lip-balm-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-lip-balm-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"164\",\"168\",\"173\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(171, 'Lip Gloss Boxes', 'lip-gloss-boxes', 'Lip Gloss Boxes', 'Lip Gloss Boxes', 'Lip Gloss Boxes', '<p>Lip Gloss Boxes</p>', '<p>Lip Gloss Boxes</p>', 'lip-gloss-packaging.jpg', 'Lip Gloss Boxes', '[\"custom-lip-gloss-boxes.jpg\",\"lip-gloss-boxes.jpg\",\"lip-gloss-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-lip-gloss-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"172\",\"173\",\"174\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(172, 'Lipstick Boxes', 'lipstick-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes manufactures the most dynamic lipstick boxes. These boxes are made using eco-friendly materials.', 'Lipstick Boxes', 'Lipstick Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Lipstick boxes are an essential need of cosmetic brands. PremiumBoxes offers the finest customization options, including the choice of shape, design, size, and style for these boxes. Various finishing and lamination options are available for these boxes. A die-cut window or a placeholder can also be added to them. They are made with sustainable materials such as cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks. CMYK and PMS color schemes are used for printing these boxes. Volume discounts are offered on larger orders.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes is among the best&nbsp;<strong>lipstick packaging manufacturers&nbsp;</strong>in the United States of America. Our packaging solutions are dynamic and perfectly designed as per the needs of the clients.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Sustainable Packaging</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Lipstick boxes&nbsp;</strong>are manufactured with organic materials. We fulfill our corporate social responsibility by providing recyclable packaging solutions. Biodegradable inks are used for their printing.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>End to End Customizations</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers end-to-end customization options for&nbsp;<strong>lipstick packaging.&nbsp;</strong>Customizations in shape, size, and style are offered to the clients.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Superior Printing</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our printing technologies are the best to fulfill the needs of clients. The options of CMYK and PMS color schemes are offered, along with 2D and 3D mockups.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Satisfactory Customer Service</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes has the best customer service for the clients at every step. Our support team is ready to help you via a dedicated chat portal, e-mail, and call. The option of call back is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We strive to provide maximum benefit to the clients by providing free shipping across North America. Shipping for international clients is also available.</span></p>', 'lip-stick-boxes.jpg', 'Lipstick Boxes', '[\"customized-lipstick-boxes.jpg\",\"lip-stick-boxes.jpg\",\"lipstick-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-lipstick-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"170\",\"174\",\"175\",\"176\"]', 1, 1),
(173, 'Lotion Boxes', 'lotion-boxes', 'Cosmetics brands need lotion boxes for their product safety and appropriate presentation in the market. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes at the lowest prices.', 'Lotion Boxes', 'Lotion Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Lotion boxes are specifically designed for the protection of delicate lotions. Clients can get them in customizable shapes and styles. A variety of printing options are available for these boxes. The inks used for their printing are plant-based. PremiumBoxes offers exciting finishing options such as embossing, debossing, glossy, matte, and foiling. Organic materials like cardboard, corrugated, or Kraft stock are used for the manufacturing of these boxes. Volume discounts are available for large orders of these boxes.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The Best Customization Options</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Lotion boxes play a vital role in presenting the products. PremiumBoxes offers packaging solutions manufactured with eco-friendly materials. We provide many customization options for these boxes. We also offer various types of add-ons for custom lotion packaging.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Design Support</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide free of cost professional assistance to our clients for designing these packaging solutions. The clients can get a fresh design as well as get changes in an existing design.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Multiple Finishing Options</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Exciting finishing options such as spot UV, gloss, matte, foil stamping, and many more are available for lotion packaging. The clients can choose as per their preference or seek professional assistance from us in this regard.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Budget-friendly Prices</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the most economical prices for these boxes as compared to the market. Volume discounts are also available. Moreover, all the transactions are made through secure payment channels.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free Shipping</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers free-of-cost doorstep delivery of these boxes for customers across North America. Shipping for international clients is also available on demand. The clients can also track their order once it is dispatched.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Professional Customer Care Services</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer professional customer care services to facilitate the clients. E-mail, dedicated chat portal, call, and a callback request are the ways to get connected with us.</span></p>', 'custom-lotion-boxes.jpg', 'Lotion Boxes', '[\"custom-lotion-boxes.jpg\",\"lotion-boxes.jpg\",\"lotion-packaging.jpg\",\"printed-lotion-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"165\",\"175\",\"176\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(174, 'Makeup Boxes', 'makeup-boxes', 'Makeup boxes are among the most selling packaging solutions. Get these boxes with exceptional customization features from PremiumBoxes.', 'Makeup Boxes', 'Makeup Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Makeup boxes have various unique features specifically designed for organizing makeup items. Organic materials like cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks are used to manufacture them. Add-ons such as handles, placeholders, trays, and dividers can also be added to improve products&rsquo; safety. Vivid printing gives a more exciting look to these boxes. Finishing and laminations including soft-touch, smudge-free, gloss, matte, and spot UV are available. Free design support, free doorstep delivery, and volume discounts are also offered for these boxes.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">With the growing cosmetics industry, the demand for&nbsp;<strong>makeup boxes&nbsp;</strong>is rising. PremiumBoxes understands the needs of the clients and offers the finest packaging solutions at affordable pricing and many other exciting features.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Enticing customizations options</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides numerous customization options for&nbsp;<strong>custom makeup boxes</strong>. We manufacture them in customizable sizes and shapes as per the need of the clients. The clients can also choose the thickness and quality of the manufacturing materials for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Add-ons</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Add-ons are an essential part of&nbsp;<strong>makeup storage boxes</strong>. PremiumBoxes offers numerous add-ons such as handles, trays, holders, and dividers for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free shipping</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide free-of-cost shipping for these packaging solutions across North America. Shipping for clients in other parts of the world is also available on request. Rush delivery option is also available on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Printing with design support</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the best printing options along with 2D or 3D mockups. Complimentary design support is also available for the clients.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable for everyone</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes strives to keep the pricing for these boxes the lowest in the market. We also offer volume discounts on large orders.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Get connected with us</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We are available to facilitate the clients at every step. Get connected with us via a dedicated chat portal, call, or e-mail.</span></p>', 'cardboard-makeup-boxes.jpg', 'Makeup Boxes', '[\"cardboard-makeup-boxes.jpg\",\"customized-makeup-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-makeup-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-printed-makeup-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"174\",\"175\",\"176\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(175, 'Mascara Boxes', 'mascara-boxes', 'Mascara boxes are the need of every cosmetics brand. A wide variety of these boxes is available at PremiumBoxes at the lowest prices.', 'Mascara Boxes', 'Mascara Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Mascara boxes are used to keep the most commonly used beautifying product safe. Their customizable shapes and styles fulfill the requirements of clients. Cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks are used for the manufacturing of these packaging solutions. Various add-ons like holders and dividers are available for these boxes. PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques along with CMYK and PMS color schemes for these boxes. Free design support, free doorstep delivery, and order tracking are available for these packaging solutions.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Exciting customization features</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Mascara boxes&nbsp;</strong>don&rsquo;t necessarily need to be black or rectangular because clients can get the most exciting customization features for them. They can choose the size, style, shape, and design of these boxes. They can also choose the type and thickness of the manufacturing material of these packaging solutions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Organic materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses eco-friendly materials such as cardboard or Kraft stock to manufacture these boxes. Inks used for printing are also derived from organic sources.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outclass finishing options</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide outstanding finishing options for&nbsp;<strong>mascara packaging.&nbsp;</strong>Spot UV, foil stamping, embossing, debossing, and matte are among the many options available for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Lowest price with special discounts</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer the lowest price for&nbsp;<strong>mascara boxes&nbsp;</strong>in the USA. Also, we offer special volume discounts on larger orders of these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-end printing techniques</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques for&nbsp;<strong>custom mascara boxes.</strong>&nbsp;PMS and CMYK color schemes are used for the printing of these boxes. We also offer free design support to clients.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Vigilant customer service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our customer care is vigilant and available to assist the customers at the earliest. Clients can reach us via e-mail, call, dedicated chat portal, or request a callback.</span></p>', 'custom-printed-mascara-boxes.jpg', 'Mascara Boxes', '[\"cardboard-mascara-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-mascara-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-printed-mascara-boxes.jpg\",\"mascara-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"164\",\"165\",\"166\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(176, 'Nail Polish Boxes', 'nail-polish-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes uses organic materials to manufacture a wide range of nail polish boxes. We provide the best customized boxes for nail polish.', 'Nail Polish Boxes', 'Nail Polish Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Nail polish boxes are always in high demand in the cosmetics industry. They are available in various customizable shapes and sizes. PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques for these boxes. Different exciting finishing options are also used to improve their aesthetics. These boxes are available at the lowest pricing along with volume discounts. Cardboard, corrugated, or Kraft stocks are used for the manufacturing of these boxes.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Nail polish boxes&nbsp;</strong>are a need of every nail polish brand. PremiumBoxes surpasses the other&nbsp;<strong>nail polish packaging suppliers&nbsp;</strong>in the market with the lowest pricing and exclusive customization options.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outstanding Customizations</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide the best options to customize these boxes as per the needs of the clients. They are available in customizable sizes, shapes, and styles.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Variety of Materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses various materials such as cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks to manufacture&nbsp;<strong>these boxes</strong>. The option to choose variations in the thickness of these materials is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Secure Payment Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses only secure payment methods for all transactions. Online transactions, cheques, and wires are the most commonly used payment methods.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>No die-cut or Plate Charges</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer these&nbsp;<strong>packaging solutions&nbsp;</strong>with no die-cut or plate charges.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Appealing Printing with Design Support</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use the latest printing techniques along with PMS and CMYK color schemes for the printing of these boxes. We also offer complimentary design support to our clients.</span></p>', 'nail-polish-boxes.jpg', 'Nail Polish Boxes', '[\"customized-nail-polish-boxes.jpg\",\"nail-polish-boxes.jpg\",\"nail-polish-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-nail-polish-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"170\",\"171\",\"174\",\"177\"]', 1, 0),
(177, 'Perfume Boxes', 'perfume-boxes', 'Perfume Boxes', 'Perfume Boxes', 'Perfume Boxes', '<p>Perfume Boxes</p>', '<p>Perfume Boxes</p>', 'perfume-boxes-wholesale.jpg', 'Perfume Boxes', '[\"customized-perfume-boxes.jpg\",\"perfume-boxes.jpg\",\"perfume-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-perfume-boxes.jpg\"]', 76, '[\"169\",\"171\",\"173\",\"174\"]', 1, 0),
(178, 'Kraft Boxes', 'kraft-boxes', 'Kraft Boxes', 'Kraft Boxes', 'Kraft Boxes', '<p>Kraft Boxes</p>', '<p>Kraft Boxes</p>', 'kraft-boxes.jpg', 'Kraft Boxes', '[\"cardboard-kraft-boxes.jpg\",\"customized-kraft-boxes.jpg\",\"kraft-boxes.jpg\",\"kraft-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 77, '[\"162\",\"163\",\"179\",\"464\"]', 1, 0);
