(179, 'Bux Board Boxes', 'bux-board-boxes', 'Bux board boxes are among the safest packaging solutions around the globe. PremiumBoxes provides the most dynamic boxes at affordable prices.', 'Bux Board Boxes', 'Bux Board Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Bux board boxes&nbsp;</strong>are used for various types of products. They are manufactured in customizable sizes and designs. PremiumBoxes uses recycled bux board to manufacture them. The latest printing techniques are used for these boxes. They are available at the lowest prices along with special discounts. Various types of add-ons like inserts and dividers can also be added to these boxes. The option of adding a die-cut window is also available.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Businesses need&nbsp;<strong>bux board boxes&nbsp;</strong>to safeguard their products. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes a wide range of safety features.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Superior Printing with Design Support</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer fascinating printing options along with complimentary design support to the clients. PMS and CMYK color schemes are used for printing.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Best Finishing Techniques</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the best finishing and lamination options such as smudge-free, spot UV, foiling, embossing, matte, and soft-touch.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Economical Prices</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer the lowest pricing for these boxes, along with volume discounts. All the payments are made via safe channels.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Sustainable Packaging Solutions</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses nature-friendly materials to manufacture&nbsp;<strong>Bux board Packaging.&nbsp;</strong>Sustainable inks are used for the printing of these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Dynamic Customization Options</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer maximum customization options for the shape, style, and size of these boxes. The option of adding die-cut windows and dividers is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outstanding Services</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Some additional exclusive services for these boxes are as following;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free doorstep delivery</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\">2D and 3D templates</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\">Exceptional customer care</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\">No die cut or plate charges</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'bux-board-boxes-wholesale.jpg', 'Bux Board Boxes', '[\"bux-board-boxes.jpg\",\"bux-board-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"cardboard-bux-board-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-bux-board-boxes.jpg\"]', 77, '[\"162\",\"163\",\"178\",\"464\"]', 1, 0),
