(183, 'Bakery Boxes', 'bakery-boxes', 'Bakery boxes are among the most excessively used packaging solutions. PremiumBoxes manufactures them with food grade materials and a lot of customizations.', 'Bakery Boxes, custom bakery boxes, wholesale bakery boxes, bakery packaging, bakery packaging supplies wholesale', 'Packaging Boxes For Baked Goods & Dessert Boxes, PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Bakery boxes are used everywhere in the world. They are used for a number of items such as cupcakes, cakes, pizzas, pies, muffins, and many more. PremiumBoxes manufactures these boxes with food-grade supplies and uses plant-based inks and adhesives. The customization options for these boxes include the choice of style, size, shape, and design. The choice of the manufacturing material is also customized, and the clients can choose it as per their preferences. The pricing of these boxes is affordable, and special discounts are also offered for larger orders.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes is one of the leading bakery packaging suppliers in the United States of America. These packaging solutions are available with customization options, free shipping, volume discounts, and design support.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The Best Customization Options</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Custom bakery boxes are available with the best customization options. The clients can get them manufactured under their desired size, shape, style, and design. Also, the choice of the manufacturing material and its thickness is available.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Go Green</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes manufactures bakery packaging with food-grade supplies. The materials used for the making of these packaging solutions are 100 percent organic and eco-friendly. Cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks are mostly used for these boxes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Affordable for Everyone</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes always strives to facilitate the clients with the finest packaging solutions at the lowest possible rates. A special discount on larger orders is also available.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Design Support</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">A complimentary design support service is available for all the clients. It includes making changes in a standard or existing design as well as making a fresh design from scratch. A 2D or 3D mockup of the design can also be shared with the clients on demand. Also, all the latest printing methods are used for the printing of these boxes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free Shipping</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free shipping is available for clients across the United States of America and Canada. Shipping for international clients is also available on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Get Connected Now!</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes always responds to the clients at the earliest. The clients can get in touch via call, e-mail, or chat support. A call-back request is also an option.</span></p>', 'bakery-boxes.jpg', 'Bakery Boxes', '[\"bakery-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-bakery-boxes.jpg\",\"eco-friendly-bakery-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-bakery-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"190\",\"192\",\"196\",\"198\"]', 1, 1),
(184, 'Truffle Boxes', 'truffle-boxes', 'Truffle Boxes', 'Truffle Boxes', 'Truffle Boxes', '<p>Truffle Boxes</p>', '<p>Truffle Boxes</p>', 'customized-truffle-boxes.jpg', 'Truffle Boxes', '[\"customized-truffle-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-truffle-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-truffle-boxes.jpg\",\"truffle-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"193\",\"194\",\"196\",\"198\"]', 1, 0),
(185, 'Tea Boxes', 'tea-boxes', 'Tea Boxes', 'Tea Boxes', 'Tea Boxes', '<p>Tea Boxes</p>', '<p>Tea Boxes</p>', 'tea-boxes.jpg', 'Tea Boxes', '[\"customized-tea-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-tea-boxes.jpg\",\"printes-tea-boxes.jpg\",\"tea-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"188\",\"192\",\"193\",\"197\"]', 1, 0),
(186, 'Snack Boxes', 'snack-boxes', 'Snack boxes are famous because of their unique shapes and attractive printing. PremiumBoxes manufactures these boxes using organic materials.', 'Snack Boxes, Custom Snack Subscription Boxes, Snack Subscription Boxes, Subscription Boxes, Snack Packaging', 'Custom Snack Subscription Boxes | Snack Packaging Boxes For Snackers', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">come in numerous shapes. They are available in all desired sizes and colors. Die-cut windows, handles, inserts, placeholders, or compartments can be added to them on demand. Their production materials are organic. Clients can choose the material as well as its thickness as per their needs. Modern printing techniques are used to enhance their appeal. Product images, brand logo, and other important information can be printed on them. Many attractive finishing options such as coatings, stamp foiling, embossing, or PVC are available. Free shipping is available for clients across North America.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Snack boxes</strong>&nbsp;play an important role in keeping snacks safe and fresh. PremiumBoxes is a well-recognized manufacturer of these boxes.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Organic Production Materials</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The manufacturing materials of&nbsp;<strong>these boxes&nbsp;</strong>are kraft, bux board, and cardboard stocks. These materials are biodegradable. Also, all the inks and adhesives used for the manufacturing of these boxes are organic.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Low-cost Packaging</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers&nbsp;<strong>snack packaging</strong>&nbsp;at highly affordable prices. Also, special discounts are available for large volume orders<span style=\"font-size:16px\">.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customization Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Multiple customization options are available for manufacturing these&nbsp;<strong>boxes</strong>. Clients can get them in any size, shape, color, and style. Many finishing options such as coatings, foiling, embossing, stamp foiling, and PVC are also available.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Finest Printing</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use innovative technologies for printing, including digital, screen, and offset printing. Clients can choose the design, color scheme, and typography to be printed on these boxes. We make sure that printing quality is satisfactory.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free shipping is available for clients across North America. Shipping is also available for international clients on request. Rush delivery is also available under certain conditions.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Design Support</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer free design support to help clients get fascinating&nbsp;<strong>snack packaging designs</strong>. Design support includes making changes in a standard design as well as making a design from scratch.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customer Care Service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide customer care service for assisting clients in matters related to packaging and printing solutions. Contact us through email, live chat, or call. A call-back request is also an option to get connected with us.</span></p>', 'customized-snack-boxes.jpg', 'Snack Boxes', '[\"customized-snack-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-snack-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-snack-boxes.jpg\",\"snack-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"187\",\"189\",\"198\",\"199\"]', 1, 0),
(187, 'Popcorn Boxes', 'popcorn-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes manufactures customizable designs of popcorn boxes. They are manufactured with eco-friendly materials. Free shipping is available.', 'Popcorn Boxes, Popcorn Packaging, Popcorn Bags, Custom Packaging, Food Boxes, Junk Food Packaging', 'Popcorn Boxes | Popcorn Packaging and Bags,  PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Many elegant designs of&nbsp;<strong>popcorn boxes</strong>&nbsp;are available at PremiumBoxes. They come in numerous customized shapes and sizes. Their manufacturing materials are durable and sustainable. They are affordable for everyone. Many additional features such as compartments or inserts can also be added to these boxes. The brand logo can be printed on them. Free design support can be availed to make these boxes more appealing. Coatings, foiling, embossing, PVC, and stamp foiling can be used on clients&rsquo; requests. Free of cost shipping across the USA and Canada is available.</span></p>', '<h1><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Inexpensive Packaging</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">We manufacture&nbsp;<strong>these boxes</strong>&nbsp;from recyclable materials. They are affordable for everyone. Also, all financial transactions are made through secure and trusted channels.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Environmentally Friendly Materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses eco-friendly materials, including kraft, cardboard, and bux board stocks. Also, all the inks and adhesives used for these boxes are eco-friendly.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Multiple Customization Options</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer many customization options. Clients can get these boxes in any shape, size, and style. A variety of finishing options are also available. Also, custom windows, handles, coatings, and other additional features can be added on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-quality Printing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">High-quality printing is essential for making&nbsp;<strong>popcorn packaging</strong>&nbsp;stand out. We offer high-quality printing using the latest technologies, including offset, screen, and digital printing. We are using PMS and CMYK color schemes. Get free-of-cost design support for making these packages appealing.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>No Shipping Charges</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Clients from North America can avail free shipping. Shipping is also available for international clients on demand. Rush delivery is also available under certain conditions.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customer Care Team</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes is assisting clients through a highly professional customer care team. Get in touch through live chat, email, and call.</span></p>', 'popcorn-boxes.jpg', 'Popcorn Boxes', '[\"custom-popcorn-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-printed-popcorn-boxes.jpg\",\"popcorn-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-popcorn-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"191\",\"192\",\"193\",\"195\"]', 1, 0),
