(190, 'Pastry Boxes', 'pastry-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes manufactures the best pastry boxes by using eco-friendly materials. These materials are known for their sustainability and perfection.', 'Pastry Boxes, Cake Slice Boxes, Boxes For Baked Goods, Bakery Boxes, Pastry Packaging', 'Pastry Boxes, Cake Slice Boxes, Boxes For Baked Goods', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Numerous alluring shapes of pastry boxes are available. They are customizable according to needs. They are available in all required sizes and colors. Various features such as handles, die-cut windows, and placeholders are added to them on demand. The manufacturing materials of these boxes are sturdy and sustainable. Clients can ask for the printing of the logo and the name of their brand on these boxes. Modern printing techniques are used for the printing of these boxes. PremiumBoxes also offers multiple finishing options such as foiling, coating, lamination, or others. Free shipping and free design support are also available for these boxes.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Pastry boxes</strong>&nbsp;are essential for keeping sweet delights safe from potential damages. They also help in presenting them beautifully. PremiumBoxes is one of the popular packaging suppliers in the United States of America for these boxes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable Price and Secure Payment Options</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our&nbsp;<strong>pastry packaging</strong>&nbsp;solutions are affordable for everyone. We also offer seasonal as well as special discounts for these packages.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Green Production Materials&nbsp;</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes considers the importance of environmental safety and uses eco-friendly materials for the production of a&nbsp;<strong>pastry box</strong>. Also, all the inks and adhesives are of organic nature.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Multiple Customization Options</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Many customizable shapes and styles of&nbsp;<strong>custom pastry boxes</strong>&nbsp;are available. They are customizable according to clients&rsquo; requirements. Die-cut windows, placeholders, inserts, and compartments can also be added on demand. We also offer multiple finishing options, including coatings, silver or gold foiling, embossing, foil stamping, lamination, and many others.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Finest Printing &amp; Free Design Support</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes offers high-quality printing by using innovative technologies along with CMYK and PMS color schemes. Offset, digital, and screen printing technologies are used for these boxes. Free design support along with 2D or 3D mockups is also available on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer free shipping for standard orders across North America. Shipping is also available for international clients. Rush delivery service is also available on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Professional Customer Care</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes offers professional customer care services. Clients can contact our professional customer care team for assistance through a live chat portal, email, or call.</span></p>', 'pastry-boxes.jpg', 'Pastry Boxes', '[\"custom-pastry-boxes.jpg\",\"pastry-boxes.jpg\",\"pastry-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-pastry-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"192\",\"195\",\"196\",\"198\"]', 1, 0),
(191, 'Noodle Boxes', 'noodle-boxes', 'Noodle boxes are popular to ensure the safety of edibles for a long time. Premiumboxes manufactures them using food-grade materials.', 'Noodle Boxes', 'Noodle Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Noodle boxes</strong>&nbsp;are used by food chains across the globe. They come in many sizes and shapes according to the needs of clients. Their manufacturing materials are durable and come in customizable thicknesses. The manufacturing materials include kraft, bux board, and cardboard stocks. Clients can get them with additional internal features such as compartments or inserts for adding disposable cutlery. Modern printing technologies are used to enhance their visual appeal. Different finishing options are used to make these boxes more tempting. Premiumboxes offers free design support and free shipping for clients across the USA and Canada.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Variety of Customization Options</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes offers numerous customizable shapes of&nbsp;<strong>noodle boxes</strong>. Clients can get them in any size and color according to their choice. Die-cut windows, placeholders, and other additional features can be added on demand. Multiple finishing options are available for enhancing their beauty. UV coating, silver or gold foiling, embossing, or other add-ons can also be added on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Environmentally Friendly Manufacturing Materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use only eco-friendly manufacturing materials. Our production materials include eco-friendly kraft, bux board, and cardboard. Also, all the inks and adhesives are of organic nature.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable Boxes</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes keeps the pricing of&nbsp;<strong>noodle box packaging the lowest</strong>&nbsp;in the market. Special volume discounts are also available. Also, we use secure and protected channels for all transactions.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Impressive Printing Quality</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We have the latest printing techniques, including offset, digital printing, and screen. Clients can choose the printing technique according to their choice. We use CMYK and PMS color schemes.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Design Support</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Clients can get free design support help to convert their ideas into reality for appealing&nbsp;<strong>noodle box</strong>.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free shipping is available for clients across Canada and the USA. Clients can also avail the service of rush delivery.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>24/7 Customer Care Service</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes provides seamless customer care services. Clients can contact us for assistance through a live chat portal, email, and call.</span></p>', 'printed-noodle-boxes.jpg', 'Noodle Boxes', '[\"customized-noodle-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-noodle-boxes.jpg\",\"noodle-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-noodle-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"188\",\"196\",\"199\",\"200\"]', 1, 0),
(192, 'Muffin Boxes', 'muffin-boxes', 'Muffin Boxes', 'Muffin Boxes', 'Muffin Boxes', '<p>Muffin Boxes</p>', '<p>Muffin Boxes</p>', 'muffin-boxes.jpg', 'Muffin Boxes', '[\"customized-muffin-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-muffin-boxes.jpg\",\"muffin-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-muffin-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"180\",\"181\",\"194\",\"198\"]', 1, 0),
(193, 'Macaron Boxes', 'macaron-boxes', 'Amazing designs of macaron boxes are available at Premiumboxes. Sturdy and eco-friendly materials are used for their manufacturing.', 'Macaron Boxes, custom macaron boxes, printed macaron boxes, printed macaron packaging', 'Macaron Boxes, Macaron Containers and Inserts Wholesale', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Macaron boxes</strong>&nbsp;are the need of every baking business across the globe. Premiumboxes is among the leading packaging brands for these boxes. They are made with eco-friendly materials such as kraft, cardboard, and bux board stocks. Various features such as inserts, compartments, die-cut windows, and handles can be added on demand. Modern printing technologies are used to make them elegant. Numerous finishing options such as coatings, foiling, or others can also be used to make them distinguished. Complimentary design support along with free shipping across the United States of America and Canada is also available for these boxes.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Variety of Customizable Shapes</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Premiumboxes offer many elegant and catchy shapes of&nbsp;<strong>macaron packaging</strong>. It comes in numerous sizes and shapes according to the needs of clients.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Green Production Materials&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Premiumboxes take care of environmental safety and use green materials for the manufacturing of&nbsp;<strong>custom macaron boxes</strong>. They include cardboard, kraft, and bux board stocks. These materials are available in variable thicknesses. Also, only biodegradable inks and adhesives are used for the manufacturing of these packaging solutions.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Low-cost Packaging</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Premiumboxes ensure to keep the pricing the lowest in the market. Also, all the payments are made through secure and trustable channels.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Numerous Add-ons</span>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Many finishing options are available for enhancing the visual appeal of these boxes. Clients may choose the finishing such as matte, glossy, foiling, embossing, debossing, and raised ink.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Free shipping is offered across Canada and the USA. Rush delivery is available on demand. Shipping for international clients is also available.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Free Design Support</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Our design experts convert the ideas of clients into reality. Free design support is available to help clients to get attractive&nbsp;<strong>macaron packaging boxes</strong>.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>24/7 Customer Care Service</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">A highly responsive customer care team is available to assist clients. Clients can contact for assistance through chat portals, email, and calls.</p>', 'macaron-packaging.jpg', 'Macaron Boxes', '[\"cardboard-macaron-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-macaron-boxes.jpg\",\"macaron-boxes.jpg\",\"macaron-packaging.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"183\",\"186\",\"188\",\"196\"]', 1, 0),
(194, 'Donuts Boxes', 'donuts-boxes', 'Many different designs of donut boxes are available at Premiumboxes. They are sturdy and ensure the safety of donuts. Get these boxes at reasonable prices.', 'donut packaging boxes, donut boxes wholesale, cheap donut boxes, mini donut boxes, donut box with window', 'Versatile Donut Boxes | Design and Print Your Logo on Box', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Numerous customized designs of donut boxes are available at Premiumboxes. Their manufacturing materials are environmentally friendly. Clients can get them in any size and color of their choice. These boxes may contain brand-related graphics and imagery. Modern printing technologies are used for the printing of these boxes. Numerous finishing options are used to make them perfect. Clients may ask for adding die-cut windows, compartments, or custom inserts in these boxes. These boxes are necessary for keeping donuts safe from dust and other damaging factors. Free shipping across the United States and Canada is available for these boxes.</span></p>', '<h1><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Economical Packaging</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers&nbsp;<strong>donut packaging</strong>&nbsp;at the lowest prices. All financial transactions are made through secure and protected channels.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Biodegradable Materials&nbsp;</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">These boxes are made using biodegradable materials. They include kraft, bux board, and cardboard stocks. The inks and adhesives used for these boxes are also organic.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Numerous Customization Options&nbsp;</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>G</strong>et many beautiful shapes and styles of these boxes following the customization options at PremiumBoxes. Custom inserts, die-cut windows, and compartments can also be added on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Impressive Printing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Modern printing technologies, along with PMS and CMYK color schemes, are used for these boxes. We also offer complimentary design support to clients to get the best&nbsp;<strong>donut packaging design for their brands</strong>.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free shipping for clients across the USA and Canada is available. Rush delivery service is also available on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>A responsive Customer Care Team</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Clients can get in touch with our dedicated customer care team at any time through email, dedicated chat portals, and calls. Also, a call-back request can be made to get in touch with us.</span></p>', 'dount-boxes.jpg', 'Donuts Boxes', '[\"custom-dount-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-printed-dount-boxes.jpg\",\"dount-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-dount-boxes.jpg\"]', 81, '[\"190\",\"193\",\"194\",\"195\"]', 1, 0),
