(205, 'Silver Foil Boxes', 'silver-foil-boxes', 'Silver foil boxes are premium yet economical packaging solutions with great popularity among different industries. PremiumBoxes offers the lowest pricing for these boxes.', 'Silver Foil Boxes', 'Silver Foil Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Silver foil boxes</strong>&nbsp;are necessary for the packaging of high-standard products. PremiumBoxes uses eco-friendly materials to manufacture them. These boxes are shipped in a flat, ready-to-assemble shape. Their styles, shapes, and designs are customizable. Also, various printing options are available to print these boxes. Clients can get this packaging at the lowest prices. Special discounts are also available on large volume orders. Add-ons such as holders, dividers, and die-cut windows are also available for these boxes. Silver foil, along with embossing or debossing, is used for the finishing of this packaging.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Eco-friendly Packaging Solutions</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">PremiumBoxes uses recyclable and biodegradable materials such as Kraft, corrugated, and cardboard socks to manufacture these boxes. Moreover, the adhesives, dyes, and inks that are used for these boxes are also biodegradable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Complimentary Design Support</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We offer complimentary design support to the clients, along with the option to get 2D or 3D. The design support includes making a fresh design from scratch as well as making changes in a standard design.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Exceptional Add-ons</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">PremiumBoxes offers various add-ons such as die-cut windows, inserts, trays, and many more for these boxes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Affordable Pricing</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Clients can get this packaging at the most affordable prices from PremiumBoxes. We use secure payment channels for all transactions. Also, discounts on large quantities are available.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>End-to-end Customizations</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We provide end-to-end customizations for the shapes and styles of&nbsp;<strong>custom silver foil boxes.&nbsp;</strong>The option to customize the thickness of their manufacturing materials is also available.</p>', 'silver-foil-box.jpg', 'Silver Foil Boxes', '[\"custom-silver-foil-boxes.jpg\",\"silver-foil-box.jpg\",\"silver-foil-boxes.jpg\",\"silver-foil-box-packaging.jpg\"]', 79, '[\"201\",\"202\",\"203\",\"204\"]', 1, 0),
