(223, 'Invitation Boxes', 'invitation-boxes', 'Invitation boxes have replaced conventional invitation techniques. PremiumBoxes offers customizable packaging with free shipping and the lowest prices.', 'Greeting Cards, Invitation Boxes, Invitations Gifts Boxes, Personalized Gifts Boxes,  invitation boxes for wedding,', 'Invitations, Stationery and Personalized Gifts Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Invitation Boxes are used for inviting guests to various events. PremiumBoxes offers different customizations in style and shapes for this packaging. It is made with cardboard, kraft, and corrugated cardboard stocks. The manufacturing material, as well as its thickness, depends upon the choice of the clients. Multiple add-ons such as holders and inserts can be added to these boxes. Special finishing techniques such as soft-touch, smudge-free, matte, gloss, and many more are used to make the packaging more appealing. Various printing options are used to print these boxes. This packaging is available at the lowest prices.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Enhanced Product Safety</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes use sturdy organic materials such as cardboard, corrugated, and Kraft stocks to manufacture these boxes. The clients can choose the thickness of the manufacturing supplies as per their preferences.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers free doorstep delivery across the USA and Canada. The option of rush delivery is also available on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Remarkable Printing Techniques</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes<strong>&nbsp;</strong>uses modern printing techniques such as screen, digital, and offset to print&nbsp;<strong>invitation packaging.&nbsp;</strong>Free design support, along with 2D and 3D mockups of the design, is available.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Fascinating Finishing Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Different finishing options such as embossing, debossing, gloss, smudge-free, etc., are available for this packaging.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable Pricing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer the best pricing for these boxes. Also, all the transactions are made through secure payment channels.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customer Care Services</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We respond at the earliest via different channels to facilitate clients. We are available at call, e-mail, and dedicated chat portals.</span></p>', 'printed-invitation-boxes.jpg', 'Invitation Boxes', '[\"custom-invitation-boxes.jpg\",\"invitation-boxes.jpg\",\"invitation-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-invitation-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"226\",\"237\",\"238\",\"243\"]', 1, 0),
(224, 'Medicine Boxes', 'medicine-boxes', 'Medicine Boxes', 'Medicine Boxes', 'Medicine Boxes', '<p>Medicine Boxes</p>', '<p>Medicine Boxes</p>', 'medicine-boxes-wholesale.jpg', 'Medicine Boxes', '[\"custom-medicine-boxes.jpg\",\"medicine-boxes.jpg\",\"medicine-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-medicine-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"230\",\"233\",\"239\",\"241\"]', 1, 0),
(225, 'Paper Boxes', 'paper-boxes', 'Paper boxes are the most economical packaging solutions all over the world. PremiumBoxes offers them with free design support and 2D and 3D mockups.', 'Paper Boxes, Nature-friendly Materials, paper packaging, die-cut window boxes', 'Paper Boxes | Two-Piece Custom Boxes | Box Packaging', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Paper boxes are used in various businesses for different purposes. PremiumBoxes provides them with a number of customization options that include the choice of style, design, shape, and size. CMYK and PMS color schemes are used for the printing of these boxes. This packaging is available at the most affordable pricing. The options of embossing, debossing, matte, and gloss are available for the finishing of these boxes. Organic materials such as Kraft and other papers are used to manufacture them.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Paper boxes&nbsp;</strong>are used for the packaging of various types of products. PremiumBoxes offers them at the lowest pricing with special discounts as well.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Nature-friendly Materials</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses organic Kraft and other papers to manufacture this packaging. Also, the inks used for their printing are completely plant-based.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>End to End Customizations</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Various customization options for the size, shape, and design of these boxes are available. The option to get a die-cut window and other add-ons added is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Latest Printing Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Vivid printing techniques are used to print the&nbsp;<strong>paper packaging</strong>. The option of choosing the color schemes from PMS and CMYK color palettes is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Superior Customer Services</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers rapid customer care services. Get connected with us through call, email, and a dedicated chat portal.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Complimentary Design Support</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides complimentary design support to clients. We also offer 2D and 3D mockups of the design on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>', 'paper-boxes.jpg', 'Paper Boxes', '[\"custom-paper-boxes.jpg\",\"paper-boxes.jpg\",\"paper-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-paper-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"221\",\"228\",\"229\",\"238\"]', 1, 0),
(226, 'Pillow Boxes', 'pillow-boxes', 'Pillow Boxes', 'Pillow Boxes', 'Pillow Boxes', '<p>Pillow Boxes</p>', '<p>Pillow Boxes</p>', 'printed-pillow-boxes.jpg', 'Pillow Boxes', '[\"customized-pillow-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-pillow-boxes.jpg\",\"pillow-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-pillow-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"220\",\"227\",\"242\",\"243\"]', 1, 0),
(227, 'Playing Card Boxes', 'playing-card-boxes', 'Elegance and compact structure can best define the playing card boxes. PremiumBoxes offers the best pricing and customization options for these boxes.', 'Playing Card Boxes,  Playing Card Tuck Boxes, Card Tuck Boxes and Cases, Card Boxes, Card Packaging', 'Playing Card Boxes | Playing Card Tuck Boxes and Cases', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Playing card boxes are the essential need of every playing card brand. They are manufactured with organic materials such as Kraft, cardboard, or paper stocks. PremiumBoxes offers the latest printing options, including offset, digital, and screen for the printing of these boxes. Customizations in shape, size, and style are available. The option to add a die-cut window and other add-ons is also available. Complimentary design support, free shipping, and special discounts are also available for these boxes.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Playing card boxes&nbsp;</strong>serve many purposes for businesses. PremiumBoxes offers the latest customizations at the most affordable pricing for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Finest Materials</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use the finest materials such as high-grade Kraft stock and cardboard to manufacture&nbsp;<strong>playing card boxes.</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Advance Printing with Design Support</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use advanced techniques such as offset, silkscreen, and digital to print these boxes. A 2D or 3D mockup of the&nbsp;<strong>playing card box template</strong>&nbsp;along with free design support is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Various Add-ons</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers different add-ons such as holders, inserts, and die-cut windows for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Latest Finishing Techniques</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Modern finishing options such as soft-touch, gloss, embossing, debossing, and foil stamping are available for this packaging.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Lowest Pricing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the most affordable pricing for these boxes. Also, all the payments are made through secure channels.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Some Exclusive Services</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides various exclusive services, which are as follows:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free of cost doorstep delivery</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Shipping for international clients</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">No charges for die-cut or plate</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Professional customer care</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'playing-card-boxes.jpg', 'Playing Card Boxes', '[\"custom-playing-card-boxes.jpg\",\"playing-card-boxes.jpg\",\"playing-card-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-playing-card-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"223\",\"234\",\"235\",\"242\"]', 1, 0),
(228, 'Postage Boxes', 'postage-boxes', 'Postage boxes are used by many businesses to deliver their products. PremiumBoxes uses rigid and materials to manufacture these boxes.', 'Postage Boxes, Eco-Friendly Packaging Boxes, Personalised Packaging Boxes, Personalised Postal Boxes', 'Postal Boxes | Personalised & Eco-Friendly Packaging Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Postage boxes are the perfect packaging solutions to ship various items. They are made with rigid and durable materials including kraft, corrugated cardboard, and bux board stocks. PremiumBoxes provides end-to-end customizations for the shape and size of this packaging. Moreover, the choice of adding a detachable lid is also available. These boxes are available at the best prices. Different printing techniques such as digital, offset, and screen is used to print them. The option of adding a die-cut window, inserts, and placeholders is available. Various finishing options are also available for these boxes.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Get Customized Packaging Solutions</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Different industries use postage boxes for shipping their products. PremiumBoxes provides the safest packaging with a number of customization options. We offer the best customizations, including shape, style, and size, along with the option to add a die-cut window. Also, the clients can choose the style of the lid to be attached or detachable.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides free shipping across the USA and Canada. Shipping for international clients is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable Pricing with Secure Payment Gateways</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers&nbsp;<strong>custom postage boxes</strong>&nbsp;at the lowest prices. Also, we use only secure payment channels for all the transactions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;<strong>Superior Finishing Options</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer various lamination and finishing options for the&nbsp;<strong>postage packaging</strong>, such as gloss, foiling, spot-UV, and many more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Eco-friendly Materials</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses only nature-friendly supplies such as corrugated, bux board, and Kraft stocks to manufacture these boxes. The option to customize the thickness of the manufacturing material is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outclass Customer Service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our customer support team professionally greets and assists the clients. We provide customer service through email, call, and dedicated chat portal along with the option of call back.</span></p>', 'postage-boxes.jpg', 'Postage Boxes', '[\"customized-postage-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-postage-boxes.jpg\",\"postage-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-postage-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"158\",\"230\",\"241\",\"242\"]', 1, 0),
(229, 'Presentation Boxes', 'presentation-boxes', 'Presentation boxes are used for showcasing the products. PremiumBoxes uses rigid materials along with various customizations to manufacture these boxes.', 'Presentation Boxes, Promotional Boxes,  Advertising Packaging', 'Promotional, Advertising & Presentation Boxes | PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Businesses need presentation boxes to present their products. PremiumBoxes uses rigid materials such as cardboard, corrugated, or Kraft stocks to manufacture these boxes. Clients can choose the shape, style, and design of these boxes as per their preferences. Various add-ons such as dividers and holders can also be added to these boxes. Different finishing techniques including embossing, debossing, foiling, smudge-free, and many more, are available for these packaging solutions.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Presentation boxes&nbsp;</strong>are used in different industries to present the products. PremiumBoxes is among the best packaging suppliers in the market for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Superior Printing Techniques</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Modern printing techniques, along with organic inks, are used to print these boxes. Also, we offer free design support for these boxes. The making of a whole new design from scratch as well as making changes in the existing one is offered. Clients can also get 2D or 3D templates of the design on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides free-of-cost shipping to clients across North America. Shipping for international clients is also available on request.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Affordable Pricing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers these boxes at the most affordable prices. Only safe and secure payment options are used for transactions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customer Service</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our professional customer care team assists the clients at every stage through a dedicated chat portal, call, or e-mail.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Choice of Materials</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses organic and eco-friendly materials such as sturdy cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks to manufacture&nbsp;<strong>presentation packaging</strong>. The clients can choose the materials as per their requirements.</span></p>', 'presentation-boxes.jpg', 'Presentation Boxes', '[\"custom-presentation-boxes.jpg\",\"presentation-boxes.jpg\",\"presentation-boxes-wholesale.jpg\",\"printed-presentation-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"211\",\"223\",\"231\",\"240\"]', 1, 0),
(230, 'Product Boxes', 'product-boxes', 'Product Boxes', 'Product Boxes', 'Product Boxes', '<p>Product Boxes</p>', '<p>Product Boxes</p>', 'product-boxes.jpg', 'Product Boxes', '[\"customized-product-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-product-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-product-boxes.jpg\",\"product-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"215\",\"218\",\"232\",\"234\"]', 1, 0),
(231, 'Pyramid Boxes', 'pyramid-boxes', 'Premiumboxes offers Pyramid boxes with amazing customization options that are famous for their exclusive shape and high-end safety features.', 'Pyramid boxes, pyramid packaging, Pyramid favor boxes, custom pyramid boxes', 'Pyramid Boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Pyramid boxes</strong>&nbsp;are unique packaging solutions that serve multiple purposes. Their distinctive shape makes them prominent and helps to provide ultimate safety to the packed commodities. They are used for a variety of products, including jewelry items, confectionary items, and gift items. They are also used to offer wedding favors. They are made with eco-friendly and food-grade materials. Their shape and size are customizable and can be molded following the needs of the customers. Generally, they are closed from all sides, but a die-cut window can be added to them. This window helps to showcase the products without opening the box.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Custom Pyramid Boxes</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The need for an exceptional packaging solution is universal.&nbsp;<strong>Pyramid boxes</strong>&nbsp;are perfect in this regard. They offer safety and also make the products look more appealing. PremiumBoxes offers these boxes amazing customization options.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Versatile Packaging Solutions</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes fulfills the packaging needs of a vast majority of customers. Our&nbsp;<strong>pyramid packaging</strong>&nbsp;is versatile and can be used for several purposes. Standard, as well as customized sizes of&nbsp;<strong>Pyramid favor boxes</strong>, are available.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-end Printing with Design Support</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques along with eco-friendly inks. We use CMYK and PMS color schemes. A free&nbsp;<strong>pyramid box template</strong>&nbsp;along with free design support is available on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Lowest Pricing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We understand that the customers look for the best packaging solutions at affordable pricing. We keep our prices for&nbsp;<strong>custom pyramid boxes</strong>&nbsp;the lowest as compared to the market. Volume discounts are offered on large order quantities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Fastest Turnaround</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes understands the importance of timeliness for a business. We try to keep the turnaround time as short as possible. A standard order is shipped in 10 to 12 business days with free shipping across the USA and Canada. Shipping for international clients is also available. Rush delivery options are also available on demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Professional Client Assistance</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our professional customer care agents are always ready to assist the customers. The customers can contact us through chat portal, e-mail, or call. A call-back request can also be made.</span></p>', 'pyramid-boxes-wholesale.jpg', 'Pyramid Boxes', '[\"custom-pyramid-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-pyramid-boxes.jpg\",\"pyramid-boxes.jpg\",\"pyramid-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"211\",\"226\",\"242\",\"243\"]', 1, 0),
(232, 'Shirt Boxes', 'shirt-boxes', 'Shirt Boxes', 'Shirt Boxes', 'Shirt Boxes', '<p>Shirt Boxes</p>', '<p>Shirt Boxes</p>', 'custom-shirt-boxes.jpg', 'Shirt Boxes', '[\"customized-shirt-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-shirt-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-shirt-boxes.jpg\",\"shirt-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"221\",\"235\",\"237\",\"238\"]', 1, 0);
INSERT INTO `product` (`product_id`, `title`, `url`, `meta_description`, `meta_tags`, `meta_title`, `description`, `long_description`, `image`, `altname`, `images`, `cat_id`, `related_product`, `status`, `show_home`) VALUES
(233, 'Sleeve Boxes', 'sleeve-boxes', 'Sleeve boxes are one of the best packaging solutions for valuable items. PremiumBoxes offers them with various customization options.', 'Sleeve Boxes, cardboard sleeve packaging, food sleeve packaging, custom sleeve boxes, sleeve packaging, custom packaging sleeves', 'Sleeve Boxes: Sleeve Packaging Free & Fast Shipping', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Sleeve boxes are considered the most protective and stylish packaging solutions. They come with a sleeve and a top lid or cover to wrap the sleeve. The sleeve and the cover are both customizable in terms of size, shape, style, and design. A die-cut window, as well as a handle, can also be added to these boxes. PremiumBoxes offers them at highly affordable pricing and special volume discounts on larger orders. These boxes are manufactured with organic supplies only. The inks and adhesives used for these boxes are also made with organic sources.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Sleeve boxes</strong>&nbsp;are used in different industries, including mobile phones, electronic gadgets, gift items, pharmaceuticals, and the food industry. PremiumBoxes is among the leading&nbsp;<strong>cardboard sleeve packaging suppliers</strong>&nbsp;in the United States of America.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-end Printing</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use the latest printing technologies for these boxes. The inks and dyes used for&nbsp;<strong>sleeve box printing</strong>&nbsp;are organic and eco-friendly. Also, we offer complimentary design support to the client. It involves making changes in an existing design as well as making a fresh design from scratch. A 2D or 3D mockup of&nbsp;<strong>sleeve packaging design</strong>&nbsp;is also shared with the client on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Customizations at their best</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers various customization options for&nbsp;<strong>sleeve packaging</strong>, considering that it is used in different business sectors. The clients can choose the shape, design, size, and style of&nbsp;<strong>custom sleeve boxes</strong>&nbsp;as per their needs.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Eco-friendly Packaging Solutions</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes understands corporate social responsibility and manufactures all the products, including&nbsp;<strong>sleeve packaging</strong>&nbsp;with organic and eco-friendly supplies only. Cardboard, kraft, corrugated, and paper stocks are used for the production of these packaging solutions. The clients can choose the manufacturing material as per their choice or seek professional assistance from us as well.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers free-of-cost doorstep delivery of the products across the USA and Canada. International clients can also get doorstep delivery on demand. Rush delivery option is also available on request.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Customer Care Service</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We always try to respond to the clients at the earliest via e-mail, call, and dedicated chat portals. A call-back request is also an option to get in touch with us.</span></p>', 'sleeve-boxes.jpg', 'Sleeve Boxes', '[\"custom-printed-sleeve-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-sleeve-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-sleeve-boxes.jpg\",\"sleeve-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"225\",\"226\",\"236\",\"239\"]', 1, 0),
(234, 'Soap Boxes', 'soap-boxes', 'Soap Boxes', 'Soap Boxes', 'Soap Boxes', '<p>Soap Boxes</p>', '<p>Soap Boxes</p>', 'soap-boxes.jpg', 'Soap Boxes', '[\"customized-soap-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-soap-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-soap-boxes.jpg\",\"soap-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"161\",\"221\",\"224\",\"227\"]', 1, 0),
(235, 'Software Boxes', 'software-boxes', 'Software Boxes', 'Software Boxes', 'Software Boxes', '<p>Software Boxes</p>', '<p>Software Boxes</p>', 'software-boxes.jpg', 'Software Boxes', '[\"custom-printed-software-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-software-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-software-boxes.jpg\",\"software-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"153\",\"158\",\"211\",\"212\"]', 1, 0),
(236, 'Sports Boxes', 'sports-boxes', 'Sports boxes are getting very popular these days. PremiumBoxes provides these packages with superior customization and finishing options.', 'Sports Boxes, sports packaging, sports box packaging, cardboard sports packaging, Sports Subscription Boxes', 'Sports Subscription Boxes | Golf Ball, Football and Shoes Box', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Sports boxes&nbsp;</strong>are specifically designed to meet the requirements of various sports items. PremiumBoxes uses sturdy materials such as corrugated, cardboard, and Kraft stocks to manufacture this packaging. Customizations in shapes and sizes of these boxes are also available. Various latest printing techniques are used to print these packages. Also, many exciting finishing options such as gloss, matte, spot-UV, and smudge-free are available. These boxes are available at the lowest prices and special volume discounts. Free shipping and complimentary design support are also available. The addition of placeholders and die cut windows is also an option.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The growing sports industry is giving rise to the demand for&nbsp;<strong>sports</strong>&nbsp;<strong>boxes.&nbsp;</strong>PremiumBoxes offers these packaging solutions with various exclusive services.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Design Support</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Complimentary design support is available for these boxes. Also, a 2D or 3D template of the design is provided on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>End to End Customizations</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers maximum customizations for&nbsp;<strong>custom sports boxes.</strong>&nbsp;The customization options involve the choice of the sizes, shapes, styles, and thickness of the materials to manufacture these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Superb Finishing Techniques</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Latest finishing and lamination options such as soft-touch, foiling, matte, and spot UV are available for&nbsp;<strong>sports packaging</strong>.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Sustainable Materials</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes<strong>&nbsp;</strong>fulfills its corporate social responsibility towards nature by using 100 percent organic materials such as cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks to manufacture&nbsp;<strong>sports packaging.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Optional Add-ons</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Various add-ons such as holders, dividers, and trays can also be added to these boxes to enhance their safety, presentation, and holding features.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>No Delivery Charges</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides free-of-cost delivery to clients in North America. Shipping for international clients is also available.</span></p>', 'custom-printed-sport-boxes.jpg', 'Sports Boxes', '[\"custom-printed-sport-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-sport-boxes.jpg\",\"sport-boxes.jpg\",\"sport-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"216\",\"230\",\"239\",\"242\"]', 1, 0),
(237, 'Suitcase Boxes', 'suitcase-boxes', 'The unique structure of the suitcase boxes makes them suitable for various products. PremiumBoxes provides them at the lowest price and free shipping across the USA.', 'Suitcase Boxes, Suitcase Packaging, Cardboard Suitcase Boxes, Cardboard Packaging, Suitcase Box Packaging', 'Decorative and Customized Suitcases Boxes, PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Suitcase boxes are the need of various industries for packaging their products. PremiumBoxes manufactures this packaging in different sizes and designs. Organic materials such as cardboard, Kraft, or corrugated stocks are used for the manufacturing of these boxes. Alluring finishing options such as embossing, debossing, foil stamping, and many more are available for these boxes. This packaging has a dedicated handle on the top panel. Also, clients can choose from various printing types to print this packaging. These boxes are available at the lowest prices, along with volume discounts on larger orders. Free doorstep delivery and free design support are also available.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Suitcase boxes&nbsp;</strong>are the packaging choice of many brands for their items. PremiumBoxes is among the top packaging suppliers in the USA for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Top-class Printing Options</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use top-class printing techniques, including silkscreen, digital, and offset printing, for the printing of these boxes. Complimentary design support, along with a 2D or 3D mockup of the design, is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Most Affordable Pricing</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes always strives to offer these boxes at the most affordable pricing. Also, all the transactions are made through secure payment channels.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Add-ons</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides the option of add-ons such as holders, inserts, and dividers for&nbsp;<strong>custom suitcase boxes</strong>.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Striking Finishing Techniques</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Striking finishing options such as gloss, foiling, soft-touch, and many more are available for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Exceptional Customer Service</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our team is readily available to assist the clients at every stage. Reach us through call, email, and a dedicated chat portal.</span></p>', 'suitcase-boxes.jpg', 'Suitcase Boxes', '[\"custom-printed-suitcase-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-suitcase-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-suitcase-boxes.jpg\",\"suitcase-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"221\",\"226\",\"233\",\"242\"]', 1, 0),
(238, 'Tie Boxes', 'tie-boxes', 'Tie boxes are stylish packaging solutions that come in many shapes and styles. PremiumBoxes offers them with dynamic printing and finishing options.', 'custom tie boxes, custom tie boxes, tie boxes wholesale, bow tie boxes wholesale, mens tie boxes', 'Neck tie boxes: Bow tie boxes wholesale, Men\'s tie boxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Tie boxes are the necessity of every clothing brand to present the item in the best way possible. PremiumBoxes manufactures these boxes with various materials such as cardboard, Kraft, corrugated stocks. The option to get variations in their thickness is also available. This packaging is available in a round, sleeve, shoulder, magnetic closure, and many more styles. Impressive finishing techniques such as gloss, embossing, foiling, and many more are used for these boxes. The option to add a die-cut window, a placeholder, or an insert is also available. Special volume discounts are also available on larger orders.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">The demand for unique&nbsp;<strong>tie boxes&nbsp;</strong>is constantly increasing in the clothing industry. PremiumBoxes provides these packages with excellent add-ons to improve their protection as well as presentation features.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Striking Customizations</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Many options are available to customize the sizes, shapes, and styles of these boxes. Also, the option of variation in the thickness of their manufacturing materials is available.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Budget-Friendly Prices</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes offers the most budget-friendly prices to manufacture these boxes. Volume discounts are also available for larger orders. Also, only secure and trusted payment channels are used for financial transactions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outclass Finishing and Lamination</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide the best finishing and lamination options such as gloss, matte, foiling, soft-touch, smudge-free, watermark, and many more for&nbsp;<strong>tie packaging.</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Various Printing Techniques</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest technologies for the printing of these packages. The option to get complimentary design support along with a 2D or 3D mockup is also available on demand.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Some Free Services</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides some additional exclusive services without any charges. These services are as follows:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">No die-cut or plate charges</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free doorstep delivery across USA and Canada</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Free order tracking</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">A call back request</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'tie-boxes.jpg', 'Tie Boxes', '[\"customized-tie-boxes.jpg\",\"custom-printed-tie-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-tie-boxes.jpg\",\"tie-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"212\",\"225\",\"228\",\"233\"]', 1, 0),
(239, 'Toy Boxes', 'toy-boxes', 'Toy boxes are pretty and creative packaging solutions. PremiumBoxes provides this packaging with end-to-end customizations and free shipping across North America.', 'Toy Boxes, Toy Storage Boxes, Kids Toy Storage Boxes, Custom Toy Packaging,  Toy Packaging', 'Kids Toy Storage Boxes | Custom Toy Packaging, PremiumBoxes', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Toy boxes are among the most sustainable packaging solutions around the globe. PremiumBoxes uses cardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks to manufacture these boxes. Their shapes, sizes, and designs are customized as per the requirements of the clients. They can also choose desired printing techniques to print these boxes. The inks, dyes, and adhesives used for these packaging solutions are organic and biodegradable. Various finishing and lamination options are available for these boxes. Add-ons such as die-cut windows, holders, and inserts are also available for these packages. Based on their shape, these packaging solutions come in a flat ready to assemble shape.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Special add-ons</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes provides various add-ons such as holders, dividers, die-cut windows, trays, inserts, dedicated handles, and many more for these boxes.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Economical Pricing</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Our pricing is the lowest as compared to the market. We also offer volume discounts to the clients. Also, we use only safe, secure, and trusted channels for all financial transactions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Vivid Printing Techniques</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes uses different techniques such as digital, silkscreen, and offset printing to print&nbsp;<strong>toy packaging</strong>. All the inks and dyes used in these printing methods are organic and biodegradable. Also,<strong>&nbsp;</strong>complimentary design support is available, along with the option to get a 2D or 3D mockup.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Nature-friendly Packaging Solutions</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">PremiumBoxes<strong>&nbsp;</strong>uses nature-friendly&nbsp;<strong>toy packaging materials such as c</strong>ardboard, Kraft, and corrugated stocks to fulfill its responsibility towards nature.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Outclass Customer Service</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We provide outstanding customer support to the clients at every step. Get in touch with us through e-mail, dedicated chat portal, and call. A call-back request is also an option to get in touch with us.</span></p>', 'toy-boxes.jpg', 'Toy Boxes', '[\"custom-toy-boxes.jpg\",\"customzied-toy-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-toy-boxes.jpg\",\"toy-boxes.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"214\",\"219\",\"222\",\"227\"]', 1, 0),
(240, 'Wedding Card Boxes', 'wedding-card-boxes', 'Wedding card boxes are famous, and Premiumboxes uses organic materials for their manufacturing. They are known for unique designs and customizable sizes.', 'Wedding Card Boxes, Card Packaging, Wedding card packaging, custom packaging, custom card boxes', 'Wedding Card Holder and Luxury Card Packaging', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes manufactures&nbsp;<strong>wedding card boxes</strong>&nbsp;with environmentally friendly materials, which include bux board, kraft, and cardboard. Many customization options are available to make these boxes fascinating. Clients can get them in various shapes, sizes, colors, and styles according to their needs. Innovative printing techniques with multiple finishing options are used to make these boxes more alluring and presentable. Die-cut windows, custom inserts, and placeholders can also be added to these boxes on demand. Free shipping is available across the USA and Canada. Free design support is also available.</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Wedding card boxes</strong>&nbsp;are essential for maintaining the beauty of wedding cards. Premiumboxes is one of the major suppliers of these boxes in the United States of America.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Green Production Materials</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>These boxes</strong>&nbsp;are made from green materials. These materials include kraft, bux board, and cardstock. They are also available in different thicknesses. Moreover, the inks and adhesives used for the manufacturing of&nbsp;<strong>custom wedding card boxes</strong>&nbsp;are also eco-friendly.&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Economical and Cost-effective Packaging</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Premiumboxes keeps the pricing the lowest to make these boxes affordable for everyone. Also, all the financial transactions are made via trustable and secure channels.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Numerous Customization Options&nbsp;</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer multiple customization choices for making&nbsp;<strong>unique wedding card boxes.&nbsp;</strong>The customization options include the choice of sizes, shapes, styles, and color schemes of the boxes.&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>High-quality Printing</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We use modern printing techniques along with PMS and CMYK color schemes. Clients can choose any printing technique from offset printing, digital printing, and screen printing according to their needs. Premiumboxes makes sure that the printing quality is always pleasing.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Free Shipping&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We offer free shipping across Canada and the USA. Shipping is also available for international clients. Rush delivery service is also available on demand.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Dedicated Customer Care Services</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">We are available to assist the clients at every step. Feel free to reach our dedicated customer care team for assistance through email, chat portals, or call.</span></p>', 'wedding-card-boxes.jpg', 'Wedding Card Boxes', '[\"customized-wedding-card-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-wedding-card-boxes.jpg\",\"wedding-card-boxes.jpg\",\"wedding-card-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"211\",\"220\",\"223\",\"242\"]', 1, 0),
