(243, 'Wrap Boxes', 'wrap-boxes', 'PremiumBoxes offers wrap boxes with end-to-end customizations and the latest printing options. These boxes are made with organic and eco-friendly supplies.', 'Gift Wrap Boxes, Wrapping Paper,  Wrapping  Paper Supplies, Gift Packaging, Packaging for gifts', 'Gift Wrap Boxes, Wrapping Paper & Wrapping Supplies', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Wrap boxes&nbsp;</strong>are necessary to package various types of products. PremiumBoxes uses excellent customization options to personalize the shapes, styles, and sizes of these boxes. Nature-friendly materials such as cardboard, corrugated, and Kraft stocks are used for their manufacturing. Various printing options such as silkscreen, offset, and digital are available to print these boxes. Also, different finishing techniques are used for this packaging. These boxes are available at affordable pricing, along with special discounts for large volume orders. Free shipping across the USA and Canada is available.</span></p>', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Variety of Customizations</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">PremiumBoxes provides different customization options for the shapes, sizes, and styles of these packaging solutions. The option to choose the materials of these boxes is also available.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Most Economic Pricing</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We offer these boxes with the most economical pricing. Also, special volume discounts are available on larger orders. All the transactions are made through safe payment gateways.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Latest Printing Techniques</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">PremiumBoxes uses the latest printing techniques to print&nbsp;<strong>wrap packaging.&nbsp;</strong>Also, we offer complimentary design support along with 2D or 3D mock-ups.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>High-class Finishing</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">High-class finishing techniques such as gloss, smudge-free, soft-touch, foiling, and many more are available for these boxes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Superior Customer Support</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">PremiumBoxes offers superior customer support through e-mail, call, and a dedicated chat portal. A call back request is also an option for the clients to get in touch with us.</p>', 'wrap-boxes.jpg', 'Wrap Boxes', '[\"customized-wrap-boxes.jpg\",\"printed-wrap-boxes.jpg\",\"wrap-boxes.jpg\",\"wrap-boxes-wholesale.jpg\"]', 67, '[\"219\",\"221\",\"228\",\"230\"]', 1, 0),
